  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/e9c573220103b68ffbd83b7804d42be4.avif?t=1753032568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras_big/e9c573220103b68ffbd83b7804d42be4.avif?t=1753032568 width=800 height=301 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infos About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash Connect 2 is a deceptivly simple puzzle game in which you have to connect all the dots. But don't be fooled by the simple appearance, difficulty ramps up quickly, as new mechanics are introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To complete a level, you have to connect all dots on your screen using your cursor. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dots can only be connected once and connections can't go through walls. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More mechanics will be revealed as you play, which make the puzzle solving more complex and levels difficult to solve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More then 40 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mindbending puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing soundscapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple mechanics, complex levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/e9c573220103b68ffbd83b7804d42be4.avif?t=1753032568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras_big/e9c573220103b68ffbd83b7804d42be4.avif?t=1753032568 width=800 height=301 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infos About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash Connect 2 is a deceptivly simple puzzle game in which you have to connect all the dots. But don't be fooled by the simple appearance, difficulty ramps up quickly, as new mechanics are introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/5c476e51d269768afd17f16141f0d005.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To complete a level, you have to connect all dots on your screen using your cursor. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dots can only be connected once and connections can't go through walls. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More mechanics will be revealed as you play, which make the puzzle solving more complex and levels difficult to solve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/6de87f801f812477623578792cb261a2.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More then 40 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mindbending puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing soundscapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple mechanics, complex levels</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.poster.avif?t=1753032568\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.webm?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2739200/extras/dc9fb1b3a25ec5bfc1a7b14edcb118ee.mp4?t=1753032568\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
